data.title: My Life in Ruins
data.meta_description: Where to watch My Life in Ruins (2009) starring Nia Vardalos, Richard Dreyfuss, Alexis Georgoulis and directed by Donald Petrie.
data.text: A Greek tour guide named Georgia attempts to recapture her kefi (Greek for mojo) by guiding a ragtag group of tourists around Greece and showing them the beauty of her native land. Along the way, she manages to open their eyes to the wonders of an exotic foreign land while beginning to see the world through a new set of eyes in the process.
